512
00:52:54.005 --> 00:52:55.507
[LIFT BELL DINGS]

513
00:53:22.826 --> 00:53:26.371
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

514
00:54:19.674 --> 00:54:21.009
- Hey!
- Yaargh!

515
00:55:27.033 --> 00:55:28.826
[HE YELLS]

516
00:55:54.561 --> 00:55:55.645
Sorry.

517
00:56:08.700 --> 00:56:10.994
Hey! Over here!

518
00:56:29.053 --> 00:56:30.179
Aargh!

519
00:57:00.543 --> 00:57:03.796
- Mister. who are you to her?
- Shut up.

520
00:57:09.010 --> 00:57:11.220
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

521
00:57:24.442 --> 00:57:27.362
Wow. nice place. Is it...

522
00:57:27.445 --> 00:57:28.571
Hey!

523
00:57:28.655 --> 00:57:30.698
- What the hell?
- Be quiet.

524
00:57:30.782 --> 00:57:32.450
- Let go of me.
- Shh!

525
00:57:35.787 --> 00:57:37.038
[WHIRRING]

526
00:57:39.123 --> 00:57:40.792
- Go.
- Where?

527
00:57:40.875 --> 00:57:42.126
- Down there.
- No way.

528
00:57:42.210 --> 00:57:44.587
You trying to get rid of me?
Well. I won't go quietly.

529
00:57:45.713 --> 00:57:47.799
What the hell is this place. huh?

530
00:57:48.841 --> 00:57:50.885
Hey. Watch it. Take it easy.

531
00:57:55.932 --> 00:57:58.935
Who are you? What do you do for a living?

532
00:58:01.562 --> 00:58:04.148
Do you really need to do that? Huh?

533
00:58:04.232 --> 00:58:05.608
What the hell?

534
00:58:10.405 --> 00:58:12.740
What was that thing anyhow?

535
00:58:14.742 --> 00:58:16.327
[BEEPING]

536
00:58:16.411 --> 00:58:17.996
It's a time bomb.

537
00:58:18.079 --> 00:58:20.999
Tell me. why have you
been following Nancy?

538
00:58:22.000 --> 00:58:23.418
You've got to be kidding.

539
00:58:23.501 --> 00:58:25.712
You don't have to kill me to get my girl.

540
00:58:27.005 --> 00:58:29.757
Hey. I can't help it
if I'm super-charming.

541
00:58:30.758 --> 00:58:33.011
You're not a student at the university.

542
00:58:33.094 --> 00:58:35.930
The ladyboy at Rick's place. It was you.

543
00:58:36.014 --> 00:58:37.849
Yes. it's true.

544
00:58:37.932 --> 00:58:40.727
But what does any of this
have to do with Nancy?

545
00:58:40.810 --> 00:58:43.312
All I did was get back
what was mine to begin with.

546
00:58:43.396 --> 00:58:45.356
What belongs to you?

547
00:58:45.440 --> 00:58:48.067
- What is it?
- Things that belong to the rich.

548
00:58:48.151 --> 00:58:49.902
I'm like Robin Hood. okay?

549
00:58:49.986 --> 00:58:51.571
It's stealing.

550
00:58:51.654 --> 00:58:54.949
You're a lazy young boy.
You're just a thief.

551
00:58:55.033 --> 00:58:58.286
Rick's a thief anyway. And he's a dick.

552
00:58:59.370 --> 00:59:01.748
[TIMER CONTINUES BEEPING]

553
00:59:01.831 --> 00:59:04.876
What does that have to do with Nancy?

554
00:59:04.959 --> 00:59:08.796
When I was going through Rick's safe.
Nancy's library pass was in there.

555
00:59:08.880 --> 00:59:10.840
I was curious about her.

556
00:59:10.923 --> 00:59:13.968
And then she just captivated me.

557
00:59:14.052 --> 00:59:17.180
And I fell... in love.

558
00:59:18.097 --> 00:59:19.891
[BEEPING STOPS]

559
00:59:19.974 --> 00:59:22.101
I've told you everything.

560
00:59:22.185 --> 00:59:25.855
So would you please remove the bomb now?

561
00:59:25.938 --> 00:59:27.523
Vitamin B.

562
00:59:28.441 --> 00:59:30.318
Good for your health and hangovers.

563
00:59:31.319 --> 00:59:33.029
Who has a hangover?

564
00:59:33.112 --> 00:59:34.822
You think you fooled me?

565
00:59:34.906 --> 00:59:37.241
I could tell it was you under that mask.

566
00:59:37.325 --> 00:59:41.287
Don't walk away.
Who do you think you are. Spider-Man?

567
00:59:41.370 --> 00:59:43.539
Until I check your identity.
you'll have to stay here.

568
00:59:45.166 --> 00:59:46.375
Hey!

569
00:59:46.459 --> 00:59:47.960
Let me out!

570
00:59:48.044 --> 00:59:49.253
[STRAINING]

571
00:59:50.129 --> 00:59:52.006
[SUSAN] <i>Officer Lin.</i>
<i>the evidence you acquired</i>

572
00:59:52.090 --> 00:59:54.675
<i>proves transactions
between Rick and the witch.</i>

573
00:59:54.759 --> 00:59:58.054
<i>For two years. the witch has been
selling Rick Nancy's therapy videos.</i>

574
00:59:58.137 --> 01:00:00.973
<i>Clearly. Rick based his novel
off these recordings.</i>

575
01:00:01.057 --> 01:00:02.892
That's what I thought.

576
01:00:02.975 --> 01:00:05.478
Oh. I just sent you a sound file.

577
01:00:05.561 --> 01:00:08.022
Find out who this guy is.

578
01:00:09.357 --> 01:00:11.150
[DOOR CREAKS]

579
01:00:16.656 --> 01:00:18.282
[FLOORBOARDS CREAK]

580
01:00:37.051 --> 01:00:38.386
Hello?

581
01:00:40.304 --> 01:00:41.597
Hello?

582
01:01:29.478 --> 01:01:30.771
[WATCH BEEPS AND WHIRS]

583
01:01:30.855 --> 01:01:32.523
[BEEPING]

584
01:01:49.999 --> 01:01:51.834
[DOOR CREAKS]

585
01:02:11.312 --> 01:02:12.813
Oh. hey.

586
01:02:12.897 --> 01:02:15.399
How long are you gonna
keep me locked up here?

587
01:02:16.400 --> 01:02:18.611
I have human rights. Huh?

588
01:02:18.694 --> 01:02:22.448
I'll pee if you don't let me go.
Okay. you asked for it.

589
01:02:22.531 --> 01:02:24.492
[STRAINING]

590
01:02:24.575 --> 01:02:25.576
[WATCH WHIRS]

591
01:02:27.203 --> 01:02:30.206
[GROANS] Can you give me
water and food. please?

592
01:02:30.289 --> 01:02:33.292
I'm so dehydrated. I can't even pee.

593
01:02:33.376 --> 01:02:34.710
[BEEPING]

594
01:03:09.704 --> 01:03:12.164
[DR JAMES] <i>She must be protected.</i>

595
01:03:13.374 --> 01:03:15.126
<i>All my work is in her body.</i>

596
01:03:16.669 --> 01:03:20.548
<i>Someday she'll be the proof to the world
of my contribution to mankind.</i>

597
01:03:20.631 --> 01:03:23.217
[HOSPITAL MONITOR BEEPING]

598
01:03:29.765 --> 01:03:32.685
[MONITOR FLATLINES]

599
01:03:36.731 --> 01:03:39.108
[BEEPING]

600
01:03:41.193 --> 01:03:43.321
Hello? Nancy's gone.

601
01:03:44.322 --> 01:03:46.741
She just got on a plane to Tianjin.

602
01:03:46.824 --> 01:03:48.451
I think it's happening now.

603
01:03:48.534 --> 01:03:50.703
I'm going to look for her.
I'll call you from the airport.

604
01:03:50.786 --> 01:03:54.081
What happened? Release me.
Look. I can help you.

605
01:03:55.082 --> 01:03:57.918
Whatever your game is. stay away from her.

606
01:03:58.002 --> 01:04:00.755
- This is more serious than you know.
- I want to protect her.

607
01:04:00.838 --> 01:04:02.131
She doesn't need you.

608
01:04:02.214 --> 01:04:05.676
Here's the key. This door will open
automatically tomorrow.

609
01:04:05.760 --> 01:04:08.721
There's food and drink in the room.
You won't starve.

610
01:04:08.804 --> 01:04:11.182
That's dog food. There.

611
01:04:11.265 --> 01:04:13.351
Train your arms.

612
01:04:13.434 --> 01:04:14.852
Hey!

613
01:04:14.935 --> 01:04:17.104
This is an illegal detention.

614
01:04:17.188 --> 01:04:18.981
Don't go!

615
01:04:30.242 --> 01:04:32.578
[BEEPING]

616
01:05:07.822 --> 01:05:09.949
[STRAINING]

617
01:05:25.089 --> 01:05:26.674
[BEEPS]

618
01:05:26.757 --> 01:05:28.092
[CAR ALARMS BLARE]

619
01:05:28.175 --> 01:05:29.802
[EXPLOSION RUMBLES]

620
01:05:31.178 --> 01:05:32.555
Earthquake?

621
01:05:37.852 --> 01:05:39.854
[SCREAMS]

622
01:05:51.157 --> 01:05:52.992
[SUSAN] <i>Officer Lin.</i>

623
01:05:53.075 --> 01:05:55.619
Your new identity.

624
01:05:55.703 --> 01:05:57.788
The old files...

625
01:05:58.956 --> 01:06:01.417
state you and Xixi died.

626
01:06:03.711 --> 01:06:06.338
And Dr James's body...

627
01:06:06.422 --> 01:06:08.799
we had it taken care of.

628
01:06:08.883 --> 01:06:11.177
He managed to save Xixi

629
01:06:11.260 --> 01:06:14.013
with a mechanical heart
and bio-engineered blood

630
01:06:14.096 --> 01:06:16.515
that Andre tried to steal before he died.

631
01:06:16.599 --> 01:06:21.645
Inside Xixi's body are
the bio-engineered genes of Dr James.

632
01:06:21.729 --> 01:06:24.273
So far. no sign of rejection.

633
01:06:24.356 --> 01:06:27.943
The bio-engineered blood in
Xixi's body is super-regenerative.

634
01:06:29.778 --> 01:06:32.198
However. when she wakes up...

635
01:06:33.657 --> 01:06:36.076
her old memories will be gone.

636
01:06:39.830 --> 01:06:41.707
Memories of you.

637
01:06:41.790 --> 01:06:43.334
[SIGHS]

638
01:06:48.339 --> 01:06:50.591
Was the thing I blew up...

639
01:06:50.674 --> 01:06:52.801
the bioroid?

640
01:06:53.969 --> 01:06:55.554
Yeah.

641
01:06:55.638 --> 01:06:58.265
He was an experimental subject.

642
01:06:58.349 --> 01:07:00.559
Dr James called him Andre.

643
01:07:00.643 --> 01:07:03.312
His body wasn't recovered at the scene.

644
01:07:03.395 --> 01:07:05.147
We're still searching.

645
01:07:06.357 --> 01:07:07.942
Susan...

646
01:07:08.025 --> 01:07:09.527
Yes. sir.

647
01:07:09.610 --> 01:07:12.446
- Can you do me a favour?
- Of course.

648
01:07:12.530 --> 01:07:15.324
<i>Take her to an orphanage in Australia.</i>

649
01:07:15.407 --> 01:07:18.244
<i>to Director Isabella.</i>

650
01:07:18.327 --> 01:07:21.372
<i>Andre will definitely come back.</i>

651
01:07:21.455 --> 01:07:24.333
<i>I don't want Xixi to be involved.</i>

652
01:07:24.416 --> 01:07:27.002
<i>As long as she lives.</i>

653
01:07:27.086 --> 01:07:29.964
<i>I will protect her as a stranger.</i>

654
01:07:30.047 --> 01:07:35.135
<i>As her father.
her safety is all I ask for.</i>

655
01:07:50.609 --> 01:07:53.153
[SUSAN] Officer Lin.
if Xixi's memories are coming back.

656
01:07:53.237 --> 01:07:56.782
are they hers or are they Dr James's?

657
01:07:56.865 --> 01:07:58.659
That's what I worry about.

658
01:07:58.742 --> 01:08:01.787
Oh. yeah. what about the guy
I asked you to check out?

659
01:08:01.870 --> 01:08:03.998
His name is Leeson.

660
01:08:04.081 --> 01:08:05.499
He lives in Sydney.

661
01:08:05.583 --> 01:08:09.878
In 2011. he travelled to Korea.
the US and Japan.

662
01:08:09.962 --> 01:08:11.547
Then he returned to Sydney.

663
01:08:11.630 --> 01:08:15.384
He has no work records.
no family we could find.

664
01:08:15.467 --> 01:08:17.803
He was arrested for theft a year ago

665
01:08:17.886 --> 01:08:20.347
and was released due to lack of evidence.

666
01:08:21.348 --> 01:08:22.725
What did he steal?

667
01:08:22.808 --> 01:08:25.603
We don't know. His file is classified.

668
01:08:26.478 --> 01:08:28.897
We are still communicating
with Australian police.

669
01:08:30.524 --> 01:08:32.943
He's not a normal thief.

670
01:08:33.027 --> 01:08:34.778
No. We don't think so either.

671
01:08:34.862 --> 01:08:35.779
[BEEPING]

672
01:08:37.239 --> 01:08:40.576
Oh. we're losing Xixi's signal.
I think we should separate.

673
01:08:40.659 --> 01:08:43.203
Okay. That's a good idea.
I'll go back to headquarters.

674
01:09:03.474 --> 01:09:07.353
We will do everything we can
to have your identity restored.

675
01:09:12.524 --> 01:09:16.987
If I can find Xixi. I just want to
have a beautiful life with her.

676
01:09:17.988 --> 01:09:18.989
See you.

677
01:09:19.073 --> 01:09:20.032
Hey...

678
01:09:21.158 --> 01:09:22.368
Good luck. Officer.

679
01:09:24.495 --> 01:09:25.454
Mm.

680
01:09:28.040 --> 01:09:29.792
[CENTRAL LOCKING BEEPS]

681
01:09:44.890 --> 01:09:46.225
[DOOR CLOSES]

682
01:10:26.849 --> 01:10:28.016
Trust me.

683
01:10:29.643 --> 01:10:30.728
Hello?

684
01:10:40.404 --> 01:10:44.783
All my work is in her body.
Every detail is recorded in her blood.

685
01:10:44.867 --> 01:10:46.493
She must be protected.

686
01:10:46.577 --> 01:10:50.497
Someday she'll be the proof to the world
of my contribution to mankind.

687
01:11:21.695 --> 01:11:23.739
[NANCY SOBS]

688
01:11:26.867 --> 01:11:28.494
Papa!

689
01:11:42.382 --> 01:11:44.927
You've been with me all along.

690
01:12:02.528 --> 01:12:03.779
Oh. Papa!

691
01:12:08.742 --> 01:12:10.410
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

692
01:12:17.626 --> 01:12:19.253
[BEEPING]

693
01:12:22.422 --> 01:12:24.341
Papa!

694
01:12:24.424 --> 01:12:26.343
Papa!

695
01:12:26.426 --> 01:12:28.679
Xixi!

696
01:12:47.447 --> 01:12:48.949
Papa!

697
01:12:51.493 --> 01:12:52.578
Papa!

698
01:12:54.037 --> 01:12:54.955
Papa!

699
01:13:15.100 --> 01:13:17.227
I don't have time for this.

700
01:13:39.374 --> 01:13:40.500
[TYRES SQUEAL]

701
01:14:59.329 --> 01:15:00.831
[PANTING]

702
01:15:00.914 --> 01:15:02.332
It worked! Oh. my God.

703
01:15:22.144 --> 01:15:24.021
[BEEPING]

704
01:15:24.771 --> 01:15:26.857
Hey. that was the wrong car.

705
01:15:26.940 --> 01:15:28.442
How did you get out?

706
01:15:28.525 --> 01:15:30.402
A fitness machine is no match for me.

707
01:15:31.069 --> 01:15:32.946
If you're that good. help me to find them.

708
01:15:33.030 --> 01:15:35.615
Pay attention. I <i>am </i>helping.

709
01:15:41.455 --> 01:15:42.831
Hang on.

710
01:15:45.167 --> 01:15:46.668
[BEEPING]

711
01:15:46.752 --> 01:15:47.961
There.

712
01:15:49.379 --> 01:15:51.465
- Good job. Go back to Sydney.
- What?

713
01:15:52.466 --> 01:15:55.343
You're not very polite. Go on. then.

714
01:15:55.427 --> 01:15:58.180
Hello? They've got Nancy.
I'm sending you a location.

715
01:15:58.263 --> 01:15:59.723
- [SUSAN] <i>Got it.</i>
- Okay.

716
01:15:59.806 --> 01:16:02.434
[ENGINE STALLS]

717
01:16:14.571 --> 01:16:16.490
Good afternoon. May I help you?

718
01:16:23.538 --> 01:16:26.583
- [MAN] Please wait a minute.
- Honey. look.

719
01:16:26.666 --> 01:16:28.251
Aliens from space.

720
01:16:32.839 --> 01:16:34.049
[WHIRRING]

721
01:16:40.806 --> 01:16:42.390
Thank you.

722
01:16:42.474 --> 01:16:44.184
This way. please.

723
01:16:58.115 --> 01:16:59.699
[WHIRRING]

724
01:17:48.206 --> 01:17:50.458
No. no. no! Bastard!

725
01:17:51.418 --> 01:17:52.711
Let's roll!

726
01:17:55.672 --> 01:17:56.464
Turn here.

727
01:17:59.551 --> 01:18:01.469
[SCREAMING]

728
01:18:08.727 --> 01:18:10.228
- Susan?
- Get in.

729
01:18:27.996 --> 01:18:29.122
[BEEPS]

730
01:18:31.625 --> 01:18:35.003
[ALARM BUZZING]

731
01:18:53.980 --> 01:18:55.523
That's pretty good.

732
01:18:56.691 --> 01:18:59.402
I don't want to see more people get hurt.

733
01:18:59.486 --> 01:19:02.030
Our intel told us
they would hit this vault.

734
01:19:02.113 --> 01:19:04.950
And we know their suits are susceptible...

735
01:19:05.033 --> 01:19:06.243
to gas.

736
01:19:07.702 --> 01:19:10.288
[ALARM BUZZING]

737
01:19:42.153 --> 01:19:44.072
- Madam.
- What's this?

738
01:19:45.073 --> 01:19:46.866
This is all that we found in the safe.

739
01:19:46.950 --> 01:19:48.785
- Nothing else.
- Just a camera.

740
01:19:48.868 --> 01:19:50.495
Okay. Thank you.

741
01:19:50.578 --> 01:19:52.872
[DV CAMERA BEEPS]

742
01:20:00.755 --> 01:20:03.258
[DR JAMES]
<i>Such superior regeneration ability</i>

743
01:20:03.341 --> 01:20:07.304
<i>is attributed to the activation
of the regenerative genes from starfish.</i>

744
01:20:08.805 --> 01:20:12.017
<i>Each recombined cell
contains the entire genome</i>

745
01:20:12.100 --> 01:20:15.645
<i>and fuses to other tissues
to rapidly regrow the missing part.</i>

746
01:20:17.147 --> 01:20:19.566
<i>The experimental subject
is a special force</i>

747
01:20:19.649 --> 01:20:21.776
<i>exposed to heavy nuclear radiation.</i>

748
01:20:23.236 --> 01:20:26.906
He'll become the first bio-warrior
in the world if the experiment succeeds.

749
01:20:29.576 --> 01:20:31.369
[MUFFLED SCREAMS]

750
01:20:31.453 --> 01:20:33.204
[PANTING]

751
01:20:36.333 --> 01:20:38.501
[GROANING]

752
01:20:52.682 --> 01:20:55.810
[DR JAMES] We have developed
the first generation mechanical heart

753
01:20:55.894 --> 01:20:59.814
to match the rapid regeneration
feature of the bio-engineered blood.

754
01:20:59.898 --> 01:21:01.983
If the experiment succeeds.

755
01:21:02.067 --> 01:21:05.278
the bioroid with the mechanical heart
and the bio-engineered blood

756
01:21:05.362 --> 01:21:07.697
will be the immortal warrior
of the future.

757
01:21:13.578 --> 01:21:15.038
Whoa!

758
01:21:15.121 --> 01:21:17.499
If Andre got his hands on the lab records.

759
01:21:17.582 --> 01:21:20.085
he can make an army of bioroids.

760
01:21:21.086 --> 01:21:23.338
Oh... That's horrifying.

761
01:21:23.421 --> 01:21:25.131
We can't let Andre get this.

762
01:21:25.215 --> 01:21:26.758
According to our intel.

763
01:21:26.841 --> 01:21:30.720
Andre had a secret deal
with a prominent arms dealer.

764
01:21:30.804 --> 01:21:34.391
I bet this is what
they were working on together.

765
01:21:35.392 --> 01:21:37.769
This is the only thing we have
we can trade for Nancy.

766
01:21:37.852 --> 01:21:39.938
No matter what. he won't release Nancy.

767
01:21:40.021 --> 01:21:43.650
Officer Lin.
if Andre was hurt 13 years ago.

768
01:21:43.733 --> 01:21:46.694
then what he needs is a procedure.

769
01:21:46.778 --> 01:21:49.781
That means that what he needs
more than anything

770
01:21:49.864 --> 01:21:52.492
is Nancy's blood to save himself.

771
01:21:52.575 --> 01:21:56.204
The two things he needs
are Nancy and that camera.

772
01:21:56.287 --> 01:22:00.083
While we have the camera.
Nancy should be safe.

773
01:22:00.166 --> 01:22:03.628
We don't have much time.
We have to find Andre.

774
01:22:05.922 --> 01:22:08.049
I have an idea.

775
01:22:08.133 --> 01:22:10.009
- The camera.
- Oh. Ah...

776
01:22:14.973 --> 01:22:17.308
Take this camera straight to headquarters.

777
01:22:17.392 --> 01:22:18.768
Yes. ma'am.

778
01:22:44.252 --> 01:22:46.045
Hey. boss. they're back.

779
01:22:46.129 --> 01:22:47.672
[BEEPING]

780
01:22:52.510 --> 01:22:55.930
[ANDRE] You and I are actually the same.

781
01:22:57.223 --> 01:23:01.603
We're lab rats in his little experiments.

782
01:23:05.732 --> 01:23:09.486
Ah. the only difference is
you didn't get to experience

783
01:23:09.569 --> 01:23:11.821
the pain that I've suffered.

784
01:23:13.698 --> 01:23:15.241
That sly fox...

785
01:23:17.911 --> 01:23:21.581
hiding his life's work inside of you.

786
01:23:26.127 --> 01:23:29.547
And all these years. just to find...

787
01:23:29.631 --> 01:23:30.840
you.

788
01:23:33.426 --> 01:23:36.596
I feel like you've turned me
into a monster.

789
01:23:36.679 --> 01:23:38.806
[CHUCKLES]

790
01:23:45.188 --> 01:23:47.649
[ENGINES ROAR]

791
01:24:03.331 --> 01:24:06.834
[COMPUTER] <i>Diverter initiated.</i>
<i>Purification in process.</i>

792
01:24:10.630 --> 01:24:12.757
[WHIRRING]

793
01:24:24.561 --> 01:24:26.646
Who are you? Oh!

794
01:24:29.649 --> 01:24:32.610
[ANDRE] We have the same mechanical heart.

795
01:24:32.694 --> 01:24:35.655
But I'm getting eaten alive
by my own cells.

796
01:24:37.532 --> 01:24:40.159
Thanks to Dr James's blood.

797
01:24:40.243 --> 01:24:42.996
not only will I get my powers back.

798
01:24:43.079 --> 01:24:47.125
but your blood will give me
the ability to regenerate.

799
01:24:48.501 --> 01:24:52.130
The world's first super bio-warrior.

800
01:24:52.213 --> 01:24:57.051
My blood contains two sets
of memories for 13 years.

801
01:24:59.387 --> 01:25:03.641
Those painful memories
constantly torture me day by day.

802
01:25:06.352 --> 01:25:10.398
You will have three memories
once I pass them on to you.

803
01:25:12.150 --> 01:25:15.403
And believe me. you will go insane.

804
01:25:17.780 --> 01:25:18.615
No.

805
01:25:19.407 --> 01:25:21.159
You see this diverter here?

806
01:25:22.201 --> 01:25:24.829
It'll remove all the impurities
in your blood.

807
01:25:25.872 --> 01:25:30.126
Never again
will I experience any more pain.

808
01:25:36.382 --> 01:25:38.176
What's that?

809
01:25:39.302 --> 01:25:41.220
- Quiet down.
- Hmm!

810
01:25:43.056 --> 01:25:45.308
- Mmm?
- Second floor.

811
01:25:45.391 --> 01:25:47.477
Let's go.

812
01:26:06.746 --> 01:26:09.040
- Where's the Asian girl?
- Inside the lab.

813
01:26:09.123 --> 01:26:10.291
Open the door.

814
01:26:20.677 --> 01:26:22.387
What are you guys doing?

815
01:26:24.389 --> 01:26:25.390
Nancy!

816
01:26:25.973 --> 01:26:27.684
Where do you think you're going? Agh!

817
01:26:27.767 --> 01:26:30.353
- Shaun! Sound the alarm!
- [SHOUTING]

818
01:26:30.436 --> 01:26:32.021
Get out of here! Go. go. go. go!

819
01:26:34.148 --> 01:26:35.817
Nancy! Nancy!

820
01:26:44.826 --> 01:26:46.744
- [LIN] Nancy!
- [SUSAN] How do we open this?

821
01:26:46.828 --> 01:26:49.497
- Nancy!
- How do we get in?

822
01:26:51.582 --> 01:26:52.500
Get back!

823
01:27:15.148 --> 01:27:16.399
Papa.

824
01:27:24.365 --> 01:27:26.451
Aagh! [GROANS]

825
01:27:26.534 --> 01:27:28.619
- Open it. now!
- Only the boss can do that.

826
01:27:28.703 --> 01:27:29.495
Fuck you!

827
01:28:31.641 --> 01:28:32.642
[BEEPS]

828
01:30:04.692 --> 01:30:06.736
No. it's me! It's me!

829
01:30:06.819 --> 01:30:08.946
I was trying to help.
but my gun was out of power.

830
01:30:11.991 --> 01:30:13.200
Uhh!

831
01:30:19.582 --> 01:30:21.208
[GROANS]

832
01:30:26.422 --> 01:30:29.216
I'm going to enjoy killing you.

833
01:30:50.863 --> 01:30:52.281
Yaargh!

834
01:30:55.785 --> 01:30:57.495
On three. we attack.

835
01:30:57.578 --> 01:30:59.330
Hey! I haven't even counted!

836
01:31:02.041 --> 01:31:03.334
Yaargh!

837
01:31:03.417 --> 01:31:04.460
Yaaaaah!

838
01:31:52.758 --> 01:31:54.969
[INHALES]

839
01:31:55.052 --> 01:31:58.222
[COMPUTER]
<i>Blood transfusion interrupted. reverting.</i>

840
01:32:18.951 --> 01:32:20.244
[METAL SNAPPING]

841
01:32:38.554 --> 01:32:39.972
[STRAINING]

842
01:32:42.433 --> 01:32:43.893
[LIN GASPS]

843
01:33:01.869 --> 01:33:03.370
Goodbye!

844
01:33:10.044 --> 01:33:11.712
[NANCY YELLS]

845
01:33:33.901 --> 01:33:34.777
Aagh!

846
01:33:38.697 --> 01:33:40.282
[SCREAMS]

847
01:33:41.784 --> 01:33:42.785
Come and help me!

848
01:33:43.369 --> 01:33:44.119
Okay.

849
01:33:51.168 --> 01:33:53.254
[STRAINING]

850
01:33:53.337 --> 01:33:55.005
[EXPLOSION RUMBLES]

851
01:33:55.089 --> 01:33:57.508
[COMPUTER] <i>Warning. system malfunctioning.</i>

852
01:33:58.676 --> 01:34:00.886
<i>All personnel evacuate.</i>

853
01:34:02.513 --> 01:34:05.266
<i>Warning. system malfunctioning.</i>

854
01:34:06.308 --> 01:34:07.935
<i>All personnel evacuate.</i>

855
01:34:10.104 --> 01:34:11.689
<i>Warning. system malfunctioning.</i>

856
01:34:12.690 --> 01:34:14.692
- Officer Lin! Are you okay?
- Aagh!

857
01:34:14.775 --> 01:34:17.611
- Let's go!
- It's gonna explode! Run!

858
01:34:17.695 --> 01:34:20.739
<i>- Warning. system malfunctioning.</i>
- Run! Hurry!

859
01:34:20.823 --> 01:34:23.242
<i>All personnel evacuate.</i>

860
01:34:38.883 --> 01:34:40.426
Leeson!

861
01:34:42.261 --> 01:34:43.345
[LIN] Go!

862
01:34:43.429 --> 01:34:45.514
Go. hurry!

863
01:35:15.544 --> 01:35:18.464
[LIN] It's going to crash!
Get the parachutes!

864
01:35:18.547 --> 01:35:20.007
-Okay
-Hurry!

865
01:35:21.425 --> 01:35:22.760
Papa.

866
01:35:22.843 --> 01:35:24.053
Papa is fine.

867
01:35:24.136 --> 01:35:26.221
Don't worry.

868
01:35:26.305 --> 01:35:28.641
Susan! Strap her in!

869
01:35:28.724 --> 01:35:30.809
Don't ever leave me again.

870
01:35:33.520 --> 01:35:34.563
Aagh!

871
01:35:43.155 --> 01:35:45.616
Get her out of here!

872
01:35:45.699 --> 01:35:47.409
[NANCY SCREAMS]

873
01:36:02.967 --> 01:36:08.138
[NANCY] <i>Papa. Papa. When I get well.</i>
<i>will you take me on the merry-go-round?</i>

874
01:36:09.765 --> 01:36:11.517
[DR JAMES]<i> I don't have much time left.</i>

875
01:36:11.600 --> 01:36:13.852
<i>The bio-engineered blood
of my biggest success</i>

876
01:36:13.936 --> 01:36:16.063
<i>was all given to Xixi.</i>

877
01:36:16.146 --> 01:36:18.732
<i>It has superior regeneration capability.</i>

878
01:36:19.525 --> 01:36:21.485
<i>Take good care of her.</i>

879
01:36:49.680 --> 01:36:51.306
[STRAINING]

880
01:36:52.725 --> 01:36:55.936
Aaaaagh!

881
01:36:58.022 --> 01:37:00.315
Huh! Huh! Huh! Huh!

882
01:37:00.399 --> 01:37:02.693
Huh! Huh! Huh!

883
01:37:02.776 --> 01:37:05.070
- Huh!
- Ooargh!

884
01:37:23.213 --> 01:37:25.049
Whoooa!

885
01:37:25.132 --> 01:37:26.425
Aaaagh!

886
01:37:45.778 --> 01:37:48.280
[NANCY] Papa! Papa!

887
01:37:48.363 --> 01:37:50.657
Susan. do something! Save him!

888
01:37:50.741 --> 01:37:53.327
Pull the black handle
on your left when I say.

889
01:37:53.410 --> 01:37:54.286
Uh-huh.

890
01:37:57.748 --> 01:37:58.874
Now!

891
01:38:14.848 --> 01:38:17.601
[GENTLE PIANO MUSIC]

892
01:38:44.086 --> 01:38:46.130
- [HE GASPS]
- Papa!

893
01:38:46.213 --> 01:38:47.464
Xixi!

894
01:38:52.553 --> 01:38:53.971
Papa.

895
01:38:54.054 --> 01:38:56.181
Papa's fine. It's okay.

896
01:38:56.265 --> 01:38:58.517
[MOBILE PHONE RINGS]

897
01:38:58.600 --> 01:39:00.894
- Hello?
- [MAN] <i>Sir. the lab records are missing.</i>

898
01:39:00.978 --> 01:39:03.272
- What? The camera's missing.
- Huh?

899
01:39:09.945 --> 01:39:11.905
[LAUGHTER]

900
01:39:11.989 --> 01:39:13.379
[LIN] Hi!

901
01:39:18.551 --> 01:39:21.202
[NANCY GIGGLES]

902
01:39:35.759 --> 01:39:38.019
[LIN SIGHS]

903
01:39:39.975 --> 01:39:41.594
- [LIN] I'm dizzy.
- Papa. let's try that one.

904
01:39:41.644 --> 01:39:43.479
- [LIN] Which one?
- Over there.

905
01:39:43.563 --> 01:39:45.815
- That one.
- No. no. no. my heart can't.

906
01:39:45.899 --> 01:39:49.194
- Please.
- Xixi. I'll go. I like that one.

907
01:39:49.277 --> 01:39:52.947
All right. You go sit down over there.
I'm gonna get some ice cream.

908
01:39:53.031 --> 01:39:54.741
- Oh. I want chocolate.
- Okay.

909
01:39:54.824 --> 01:39:57.076
- I need to sit down.
- Right here.

910
01:39:57.160 --> 01:39:59.829
- I was shooting like this...
- [SUSAN LAUGHS]

911
01:39:59.913 --> 01:40:02.248
- Backward.
- I knew you'd be dizzy.

912
01:40:04.959 --> 01:40:07.337
It's just like a dream. Pinch me.

913
01:40:08.755 --> 01:40:11.799
I won't do that. You'll wake up.

914
01:40:11.883 --> 01:40:14.928
You've been waiting for this for 13 years.

915
01:40:15.011 --> 01:40:16.554
I'm happy for you.

916
01:40:26.688 --> 01:40:29.024
Officer Lin. headquarters just called.

917
01:40:29.107 --> 01:40:31.109
We know Leeson's true identity.

918
01:40:31.193 --> 01:40:33.487
His real name is Choi Kyung-ho.

919
01:40:36.490 --> 01:40:41.536
His father was the arms dealer
killed 13 years ago by Andre.

920
01:40:41.620 --> 01:40:44.456
So his real motivation was to get revenge

921
01:40:44.539 --> 01:40:46.750
and take back his family assets.

922
01:40:46.833 --> 01:40:49.544
All I did was get back
what was mine to begin with.

923
01:40:51.380 --> 01:40:54.299
When his family was killed.
he was travelling abroad.

924
01:40:54.383 --> 01:40:56.260
So he survived.

925
01:40:57.761 --> 01:41:01.387
Coincidentally. he and Xixi grew up
together in the orphanage.

926
01:41:07.922 --> 01:41:10.831
[SINGING]
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

927
01:41:10.915 --> 01:41:15.427
<i>♪ Happy birthday to Nancy ♪</i>

928
01:41:15.511 --> 01:41:18.294
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

929
01:41:18.378 --> 01:41:21.034
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

930
01:41:21.118 --> 01:41:23.363
Happy birthday. Nancy.

931
01:41:32.504 --> 01:41:34.066
[NANCY] Leeson.

932
01:42:07.247 --> 01:42:09.344
Price is no problem...

933
01:42:11.316 --> 01:42:14.880
if you've got for me
what you said in the email.

934
01:42:16.306 --> 01:42:18.906
<i>Come over to my office in Moscow.</i>

935
01:42:18.990 --> 01:42:20.920
<i>We'll talk.</i>

936
01:42:21.003 --> 01:42:23.184
<i>I'll send a plane for you.</i>

937
01:42:24.694 --> 01:42:26.414
Hey. man.

938
01:42:26.497 --> 01:42:29.349
Thanks for openly discussing a price.

939
01:42:29.434 --> 01:42:31.740
Although it's a matter of trust.

940
01:42:31.824 --> 01:42:36.186
Sorry. I have a dinner date
with Jackie Chan.

941
01:42:36.270 --> 01:42:37.361
Over.

942
01:42:37.444 --> 01:42:39.331
Fuck!

943
01:42:40.305 --> 01:43:40.326
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-
